Tuesday, December 15, 1998

MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

98-206. Sasaki v. McKinnon.

Cuyahoga App. No. 71941. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of appellants’ application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court' that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the corad that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
